<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <style>
      .wrapper {
        width: 100%;
        background: #f7fafc;
        padding: 32px 0;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      }
      .content {
        max-width: 560px;
        margin: auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        padding: 32px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        text-align: left;
      }
      .logo {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .logo img {
        max-width: 180px;
        height: auto;
      }
      .title {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #1f2937;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
      }
      .text {
        font-size: 15px;
        color: #374151;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
      }
      .card {
        background: #f8fafc;
        border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 14px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .card strong {
        color: #111827;
      }
      .button-wrap {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 24px 0 10px;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background: #111827;
        color: #ffffff;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 6px;
        padding: 12px 20px;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 28px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #6b7280;
        text-align: center;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="wrapper">
      <div class="content">
        <div class="logo">
          <img
            src="cid:defined-logo"
            alt="Defined logo"
          />
        </div>

        <div class="title">We received your request</div>

        <p class="text">Hi, {{firstName}}!</p>
        <p class="text">
          Thank you for submitting the Defined form. Your request has been
          successfully received, and our team will contact you as soon as
          possible.
        </p>
        <p class="text">
          Our initial follow-up is usually made by phone, email, or WhatsApp,
          based on the details you provided.
        </p>

        <div class="card">
          <strong>Submission summary:</strong><br />
          Name: {{fullName}}<br />
          Email: {{email}}<br />
          {{#if phone}}Phone: {{phone}}<br />{{/if}}
          {{#if selectedPackage}}Package: {{selectedPackage}}<br />{{/if}}
          {{#if serviceInterest}}Service interest: {{serviceInterest}}{{/if}}
        </div>

        <div class="button-wrap">
          <a class="button" href="{{websiteUrl}}" target="_blank">Visit Defined website</a>
        </div>

        <p class="footer">
          © {{year}} Defined Lab. All rights reserved.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
